  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00476', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-097-707b521e', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-05', NULL, 'essay', '設於某實施容積移轉管制之都市，某甲擁有一筆有保存價值之建築所定著之私有
