  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00478', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-097-707b521e', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-05', NULL, 'essay', '設有土地所有權人某甲，擬將其座落在特定農業區辦竣農地重劃土地 A，開發為低
